ANTHRAX, HUMAN - KYRGYZSTAN: (BATKEN)
*************************************
A ProMED-mail post
http://www.promedmail.org
ProMED-mail is a program of the
International Society for Infectious Diseases
http://www.isid.org

Date: Tue 19 Feb 2013
Source: Kabar, Kyrgyz National News Agency [edited]
http://kabar.kg/eng/health/full/6379


A case of anthrax [has been reported] in Kara-Dobo village of Batken, the press service of the Kyrgyz Ministry of Emergency Situations reports.

According to data of the Ministry, UY, born in 1959, was hospitalized on 15 Feb 2013 in the infectious department of Uch-Korgon medical center. "At the moment the patient's condition is satisfactory. She continues to receive treatment, "the report says.

--
Communicated by:
Sabine Zentis
